## Replay events

Use `getSequencedEvents` to replay in-memory session events (for live reconnection while the VM is running), or `getSessionEvents` to replay from persisted storage (for transcript history, including when the VM is not running). See [Events](/docs/events#event-replay) for details on the difference.

